{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-12105/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-12105"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:21:05"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["handheld, mobile"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Group of workers hold up wedding dress"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-12105","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-12105"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1/dfef9509-d870-4765-8968-fdb0d9e46fba","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T15:43:25.723Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The shots of the seamstresses repairing the wedding dress alternate with those of Alma tending to Reynolds. They contrast in their lighting—the bright white of the atelier as opposed to the dark gloom of Reynolds’s sickbed—but they both represent a “mending.” Alma’s “art,” so to speak, is chaotic and destructive; she brings Reynolds low and cares for him afterward. In doing so, she herself is crafting a version of the man she loves, much as Reynolds does the same with the dresses he makes for Alma.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:51.91347753743756,118.30282861896833,1850.5158069883528,570.2495840266223"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1/2fadaf9c-a626-405a-95a3-8e82661e8d96","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T15:43:43.240Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The mannequin was another prop made custom for <em>Phantom Thread</em>, according to set decorator Véronique Melery. It was \"fitted to the sizes and features of the actresses as their characters. We ordered dozens of these mannequins from the last company that is still hand-making them in papier-mâché in France. They still produce some shapes considered as old fashioned, ladies’ bodies having changed radically since the creation of this manufacture in the 19th century” (Burg, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW244018268 BCX2\" href=\"https://www.setdecorators.org/?art=film_decor_features&amp;SHOW=SetDecor_Film_Phantom_Thread\"><u>Set Decore</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12105/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:837.8036605657238,104.72545757071543,409.71713810316135,958.4026622296174"}}}]}]}]}